            <tr>
              <td>
                <p>Timed Groupings of Amendments for Stage 3</p>
              </td>
              <td>
                <p><a href="https://www.parliament.scot/-/media/files/legislation/bills/s6-bills/scottish-languages-bill/stage-3/spbill39ags062025timed.pdf">SP Bill 39A-G Scottish Languages Bill [timed groupings of amendments for stage 3] Session 6 (2025)</a></p>
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td>
                <p>Stage 3 consideration of amendments and debate, 17 June 2025</p>
              </td>
              <td>
